name: Warung Lily & Swimming Pool
address: V57X+P72, Tamblang, Kubutambahan, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81172, Indonesia
review 1: Such a GEM! I was driving by and popped in to shelter from the rain. This is a local Warung with swimming pools. Amazing for the kids. The food and drinks are super cheap and of a great quality. I had Nasi Goreng and Fried Chicken with Sambal. In LOVE. 5 STARS
review 2: Clean, tasty, local food, locally priced. Has pool, slides and playground for children. The owners don't speak English, so best visited with a local driver.
review 3: We had chance to have a dinner in this place while we were coming back from the waterfalls. It is a small family business, the owner and his kids are the kindest and foods were super delicious with local prices. Definitely recommended!
review 4: Comfortable place, nice and cheap price ticket for swimming, available food and drink.
